extendedInfo.description: This is an icon pack for LauncherPro Plus. You must have LauncherPro installed to use this.This is a set of black and white icons based off of Honeycomb icons for use with LauncherPro. There are many icons included in addition to most system apps. I have included the following icons:BrowserCalculatorCalendarCameraVideo CameraContactsDialerEmailSMSMusicSettingsMarketGalleryBooksGmailMailMapsTalkYouTubeDesktop ClockPlumeHandcentDolphin Browser HDAstroeBayNote EverythingDropboxNewsRobRoot ExplorerCacheMateSpeedX 3D Free/ProChase MobileBarcode ScannerGoogle VoiceTitanium BackupFacebookRun KeeperPandoraTweetcasterGeicoGoogle GogglesSetCPUYellowbookROM ManagerSlacker RadioDownloadsTheme ChooserNews and Weather WidgetWordpressVoice DialerFolder OrganizerAdvanced Task Manager Free/ProSome icons appear not to be working although most or all should work now. There are known issues with SGS because they use different package names. That means this icon just isn't for you. Deal with it. I made this for me in a few minutes and am sharing out of the goodness of my heart. Please rate accordingly.To use, from the home screen, go to Menu > Preferences > Theme Settings > Icon Pack and select Honeycomb LPP BW Icon Pack. Restart LauncherPro at the prompt.
